              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Used accelerator provided the deuteron beam,",
                "with 54 microampers on target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By author:",
                "1. The reaction yield of the infinitely thick target",
                "was obtained in several runs at E/d = 5 to 30 KeV with",
                "energy step at 0.5 KeV at E/d =5 to 10 KeV and 1.0 KeV",
                "at E/d = 10 to 30 KeV. The energy step correspond to",
                "about 50 and 100 atomic layers near the surface.",
                "2. The absolute scale was obtained by normalization to",
                "revious work (see REL-REF) at 30 KeV including the",
                "effects screening where applicable. The normalization",
                "led to a value for the stoichiometric ratio.",
                "3. The resulting cross section is the weighted average",
                "of several runs."
              ]
            }
          ],
